item.description: A Brooklyn hair stylist reportedly threw their client through the window for complaining about his haircut, the New York Daily News reports. The publication says that around 3 p.m. on Thursday afternoon (May 17) at Levels Barbershop in Crown Heights, a 33-year-old customer told his stylist that he was unhappy with his haircut, and threatened to withhold payment due to the disappointing job. This infuriated the barber, who reportedly shoved the man through one of the front store windows, slicing his face open.

item.title: How Much Does Nicholas Braun Make From His New York City Bar And Restaurant Investments?
item.description: Highlights Nicholas Braun has invested his fortune and net worth into four bars and restaurants in New York City. Succession star Braun's establishments aim to provide a relaxed and enjoyable atmosphere. Braun's passion for owning a bar and restaurant stems from his childhood dreams. Celebrities are always seeking avenues to invest their fortunes, and restaurants seem to be a popular choice.

item.title: Jeff Bezos Revealed As Mysterious $500 Million Superyacht Owner
item.description: Amazon CEO Jeff Bezos has reportedly commissioned a luxury yacht worth a cool $500 million, which is set to be completed next month. According to the Evening Standard, Bezos and his partner, Lauren Sanchez, a helicopter pilot, commissioned the super yacht prior to the coronavirus crisis, which was declared a global pandemic by the World Health Organization in March 2020. Many of the details of the super yacht have yet to be confirmed, including the ship‚Äôs name.

item.title: Matilda Djerf
item.description: Matilda Djerf is a Swedish social media influencer and Instagram star who has gained a huge amount of followers and fame for her work in the digital world so far. Furthermore, Matilda is one of the famous Instagram influencers who is currently followed by more than 1.3 million fans in her Instagram account. She is known for her beautiful face and curvy body that can lure anyone who sees her pictures for the first time.

item.title: Shop the Velvet Dress Trend Worn by Cardi B and Amal Clooney
item.description: Us Weekly has affiliate partnerships. We receive compensation when you click on a link and make a purchase. Learn more! Va-va-velvet is what we‚Äôre loving these days. Cardi B‚Äòs fuschia Nicolas Jebran dress from the 2018 MTV VMAs has totally set the tone for our future evening looks. The alluring trend was also seen on Amal Clooney earlier this summer and now because of these style savvy celebs, we‚Äôre inspired to stock up on velvety designs!

item.title: Amy Robach's Ex Andrew Shue Is Dating T.J. Holmes Ex Marilee Fiebig
item.description: Former GMA3 coanchors Amy Robach and T.J. Holmes‚Äô scandalous romance first made headlines more than one year ago ‚Äî and now their ex-spouses have moved on ‚Ä¶ with each other. Multiple outlets report that Andrew Shue and Marilee Fiebig are dating. According to Page Six, which was first to break the news, the pair bonded over their shared pain after Robach and Holmes‚Äô affair. Robach, 50, was still married to Shue, 56, when photos of her getting cozy with Holmes, 46, broke the internet in November 2022.

item.title: Below Deck's Eddie Lucas Claims Cast Is 'Lowest-Paid' on Bravo
item.description: Saying goodbye, again. After confirming that he won‚Äôt be joining Captain Lee for season 10, Below Deck‚Äôs Eddie Lucas questioned his Bravo paychecks on his way out. ‚ÄúI was not invited back to do another season,‚Äù Lucas, 37, told the New York Post on Wednesday, May 11. ‚ÄúI actually didn‚Äôt even get a phone call from them saying they hired someone else ‚Äî which kind of goes to show what the production entails. Everyone on Below Deck is expendable.

item.title: Camille Yarbrough Chats Beyonce, Rihanna, State Of Black Music
item.description: What are your thoughts about women like Beyonce and Rihanna and their impact on pop culture? I think that Beyonce has had a great impact on pop culture. I like her. She‚Äôs a tremendous performer. I also think that we‚Äôve always had sisters who danced in a sexual way‚éØalways. Going back further in the culture, we have always used our complete body. We have not been afraid to use our pelvic girdle because that‚Äôs part of our culture, that‚Äôs part of our life.

item.title: Dansby Swanson Wife: Mallory Pugh Instagram, Net Worth, Parents, Salary, Boyfriend, College And Age
item.description: Mallory Pugh is a renowned American soccer player who plays as a forward for the Chicago Red Stars of the National Women‚Äôs Soccer League (NWSL). Mallory Diane Pugh was born April 29, 1998, in Littleton, Colorado to parents, Karen and Horace Pugh. Her mother was a long-distance runner while her father Horace ran track and played football. She was raised alongside her older sister Brianna in Highlands Ranch, Colorado. Mallory Pugh began playing soccer at the age of four and played club soccer with Real Colorado in the Elite Clubs National League.

item.title: Emily Ratajkowski Gushes Over Son Sylvester on His 3rd Birthday
item.description: Emily Ratajkowski can barely believe her son,Sylvester ‚ÄúSly,‚Äù is 3 years old ‚Äî and her birthday tribute to him will have fans ugly crying. ‚ÄúThis day three years ago I felt my beautiful baby‚Äôs soul come into the world and held him to my chest and my god ‚Äî how the time has flown,‚Äù Ratajkowski, 32, wrote via Instagram on Friday, March 8. ‚ÄúWitnessing Sly become the loving, curious, funny and kind person he is has been the joy of my life.

item.title: The Truth About The Tragic Death Of Elon Musk's Neuralink Monkeys

item.title: A Record-Breaking Auction Held By Phillips, In Association With Bacs & Russo, Raised $74.5 Million
item.description: Over the weekend, the auction Phillips in Association With Bacs & Russo held has reached $74.5 million, breaking multiple records worldwide. The amount collected is currently the highest ever total money collection in the watch auction history. The previous highest record before the auction took place is only at $41,496,000, which is almost half of the total amount collected by Phillips in Association With Bacs & Russo. The watch auction sale just confirmed that many people are willing to pay a hefty price just for a single watch; it is a market where money is never an issue.

item.title: Digital Marketing Consultant Robert Arloro Discusses Four Ways to Repurpose Old Blog Posts
item.description: Blogs can be a central digital marketing tool in your arsenal. One of the challenges of a blog, though, is that you have to constantly come up with new topics to write about, according to digital marketing consultant Robert Arloro. The nice part about blogs is that they can be repurposed for other digital marketing needs. Rather than coming up with completely new content, you can take old blog posts you‚Äôve already written and repackage them in a way that gives them new life.
